::Panzertron::

Panzertron's shuttle lands a little while away from the Predacon cave, the 
major stepping out. He orders the shuttle to return to base on autopilot, 
himself transforming into tank mode and riding off.

The shuttle takes off, flying back toward the Iron Fist.
